            "text": "3698 - وَ رَوَى زَيْدٌ اَلشَّحَّامُ قَالَ"
          }
        ]
      },
      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:3:2:12:20",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/2/2/20",
      "text": [
        " قَالَ لِي أَبُو عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"مَنِ اِئْتَمَنَكَ بِأَمَانَةٍ فَأَدِّهَا إِلَيْهِ وَ مَنْ خَانَكَ فَلاَ تَخُنْهُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3698 - Zayd Al-Shahham narrated that Abu Abdillah (as) said to me:\n\"Whoever entrusts you with a trust, then return it to him. And whoever betrays you, do not betray him.\""
        ]
      }
    },
